This project is a Student Registration Form.

It is built using PHP, Bootstrap, and CSS.

The form collects details like name, email, phone, course, and more.

Each input is validated using PHP conditions and loops.

Errors are shown beside the fields if data is wrong.

On success, the data is stored in a text file.

The design uses Bootstrap + custom CSS with a background image.

The form is interactive, user-friendly, and responsive.
